column1: # Daily Transaction CSV Test Fixture for Spring Batch Processing
# CardDemo Application - COBOL-to-Java Migration Test Data
# This CSV test fixture provides comprehensive transaction test data converted from
# the legacy VSAM TRANSACT dataset format to support Spring Batch daily transaction
# processing tests
# table integration testing.
# Key Features:
# - Spring Batch FlatFileItemReader compatible format
# - BigDecimal precision validation for DECIMAL(12
# - Comprehensive transaction scenarios including debits
# - PostgreSQL transaction table integration with monthly partitioning support
# - Transaction timestamp validation for date-based partition pruning
# - Merchant information processing with proper field length validation
# - Card-to-account cross-reference validation test data
# - Financial calculation accuracy testing with precise decimal arithmetic
# - Transaction type and category code validation scenarios
# - Edge case handling for boundary value testing
# CSV Schema Mapping to Transaction Entity:
# transaction_id    -> Transaction.transactionId (VARCHAR(16))
# transaction_type  -> Transaction.transactionType (VARCHAR(2))
# category_code     -> Transaction.categoryCode (VARCHAR(4))
# source           -> Transaction.source (VARCHAR(10))
# description      -> Transaction.description (VARCHAR(100))
# amount           -> Transaction.amount (DECIMAL(12
# merchant_id      -> Transaction.merchantId (VARCHAR(9))
# merchant_name    -> Transaction.merchantName (VARCHAR(50))
# merchant_city    -> Transaction.merchantCity (VARCHAR(50))
# merchant_zip     -> Transaction.merchantZip (VARCHAR(10))
# card_number      -> Transaction.cardNumber (VARCHAR(16))
# original_timestamp    -> Transaction.originalTimestamp (TIMESTAMP)
# processing_timestamp  -> Transaction.processingTimestamp (TIMESTAMP)
# Test Scenarios Covered:
# 1. Purchase Transactions - POS Terminal and Online Processing
# 2. Return Transactions - Operator Initiated Credit Processing
# 3. ATM Transactions - Cash Withdrawal and Balance Inquiry
# 4. Bill Payment Processing - Automated and Manual Processing
# 5. Balance Transfer Operations - Account-to-Account Transfers
# 6. Interest Calculation Scenarios - Monthly Interest Processing
# 7. Fee Assessment Processing - Maintenance and Overdraft Fees
# 8. Foreign Transaction Processing - Currency Exchange Scenarios
# 9. Chargeback and Dispute Processing - Reversal Transactions
# 10. Batch Settlement Processing - End-of-Day Reconciliation
# BigDecimal Precision Test Cases:
# - Maximum precision amounts: 999999999.99
# - Minimum precision amounts: 0.01
# - Negative amounts for credit transactions
# - Zero amounts for balance inquiries
# - High-precision decimal calculations
# - Currency rounding validation scenarios
# PostgreSQL Partitioning Test Data:
# - Transactions spread across multiple months for partition testing
# - 2024-06 partition: June 2024 transactions
# - 2024-07 partition: July 2024 transactions
# - 2024-08 partition: August 2024 transactions
# - Cross-partition query testing scenarios
# - Partition pruning optimization validation
# Card-to-Account Mapping Test Scenarios:
# - Valid card numbers with corresponding account relationships
# - Multiple cards per account testing
# - Account balance validation scenarios
# - Credit limit enforcement testing
# - Cross-reference integrity validation
